parts.text: *Ach, mein Gott!*  Another casualty of war!  *So tragic!*  But... *so interesting!*  The cause of death?  *Many* possibilities! Perhaps a stray rocket?  A poorly aimed grenade? Or perhaps... *a particularly vicious case of... spontaneous combustion?*  The possibilities are endless, mein friend!  It's like a medical mystery!  *Ahahahaha!*  I must examine the body!  More data for ze science!
